plz, can someone explain me the meaning of 3 different torents for the same game release? i think it should be better to first check all released games and their torrents before we post a new torrent. posting 1 torrent for 1 game release will combine the power of all downloaders so that we all get higher download speed. and the tracker server wouldn't get that much data to work it out, the tracker must not be so heavy loaded with 3 torrents for the same game. 

come on, guys. don't be lousy to check first all torrents before posting new ones. i think the webmaster have to take some action.
